SUBDIRECTORY assert

The example in this subdirectory is referenced in the
User Manual.

assert.occ	Coding example - asserting reset/analyse, setting error on
		a B004 or similar.

This example can be compiled for any 32-bit processor by writing:

	imakef assert.tah
	make -f assert.mak

Or, equivalently:

	oc assert -ta -h -o assert.tah 

When using an MS-DOS or VMS system, replace '-' by '/'

